<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很快，<delay8 />这座<tag a="110" b="32" />的
首次大型活动就要开始了。<delay20 />
大家都在热议这件事，<delay8 />你听说了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻，<delay20 />真是令人期待啊！<delay frames="40" />
让我们一起来炒热气氛，<delay8 />
把活动办好吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就在明天，<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="33" />的第一个大型活动<delay8 />
终于要举办啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可得鼓起干劲，<delay8 />
要让这个活动热闹起来才行～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个周六有钓鱼大赛哦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你当然也会参加的，<delay20 />对不对？<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />钓鱼不用跑来跑去，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也不会累得满头大汗，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />简直是最适合我了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是钓鱼大赛了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已经准备齐全了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我呀，<delay20 />昨天就已经搜罗了
所有需要的道具。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />话虽如此，<delay20 />
其实也就只有一根钓竿而已啦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这周六是捕虫大赛呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />老实说，<delay8 />我其实
不太擅长捕虫，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我一定会竭尽全力的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是捕虫大赛了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也按照自己的步调<delay8 />
尽量努力吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">哎，<delay8 />我跟你说，<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是烟花大会了！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难得的一场活动，<delay8 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好好打扮一番去享受吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已经<delay8 />做好准备了吗？<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天早上，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快乐家协会就会对我们的家做出评价了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />收拾房间，或者装点一下<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可要抓紧<delay8 />
这最后的机会了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
从快乐家协会发回来的评价，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已经看过了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得这份居住评价简直就像一面镜子。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然自己心里也清楚，<delay8 />
一定要认真接受它<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来今年应该也能安然度过了……<10_4 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的，<delay8 />这一年过得实在太快啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过换个角度想，这也证明我过得很开心吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay20 />今年也该有始有终才行。<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最后一天就去广场上，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和大家一起倒计时吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">明天，<tag a="90" b="27" />年就结束了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总感觉有些不踏实<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然如此，那就在倒计时的祭典上<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />彻底给今年画上句点，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再用放空的心态去迎接新年吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就快到5月了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />也就是说……<delay20 />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很快就是劳动节啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />劳动节的活动<delay8 />会在别的岛上举办。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />好期待5月1日啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">今天是4月30日<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天哪！<delay20 />明天不就是劳动节了吗？！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />记得去找<colour id="3" />狸克<colour id="65535" />领取<colour id="1" />劳动节旅行券<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
不然是进不去活动会场的哦！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来，<delay8 />明天必须去一趟<colour id="1" />服务处<colour id="65535" />呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你还记得<delay20 />10月31日是什么日子吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没错，<delay20 />是万圣节。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到了当天，<tag a="110" b="32" />上的大家<delay8 />都会想问你
讨要糖果的，<delay20 />建议你趁现在
多多准备一些<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />会比较好哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶？<delay20 />你问要是没有好好准备会怎么样？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你如果好奇的话，就实际去感受一下如何？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />从失败中学习<delay8 />也是人生的一部分。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天终于就是万圣节了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />我在乔装打扮上下了不少工夫，<delay8 />
你就期待一下节日当天的我吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话说回来，<delay20 />万圣节必不可少的糖果，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你准备好了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也盼望着<delay8 />
能够从你手中收到糖果，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拜托你准备好我的那份哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">哎，<delay8 />你知道吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />马上感恩节就要到来了！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />毕竟一流主厨
来这座<tag a="110" b="32" />的机会相当少有，<delay8 />
我从现在起就特别期待了！<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但又因为是难得的庆典，<delay8 />
所以我也想自己做做菜呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀！<delay frames="40" />我真是太期待了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你有时间来参加明天的
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感恩节活动吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我当然打算参加！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我明天不是在广场上就是在家里，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是能见到你，我会很高兴的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我说，<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="30" />
马上就要到平安夜了呀！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />过圣诞节可少不了交换礼物。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我正在思考<delay8 />该送你<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什么礼物才好，<delay frames="40" />
所以你也要准备好<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送我的礼物哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">终于，明天就是平安夜了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你做好交换礼物的准备了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要把礼物包装好才可以哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我找到了一件<delay8 />很不错的礼物，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就好好期待吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>